  "number": 737,
  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/737",
  "title": "Use of active class and templates",
  "body": "In the example I see a widget with an active class defined but the widget also uses a custom template, see:\nhttps://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/blob/master/docs/examples/e-commerce/search.js#L100\n\nI tested this and the template is overruling the active class (see https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/blob/master/docs/examples/e-commerce/search.js#L51).\nI think this is the right behaviour, but maybe clean up the example so it is more clear which active class is working.\n\nLet me know, I would love the send in a PR.\n",
